comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of LAL possession is confirmed.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Young (LAL) after making the pass.
Chandler (DEN) makes contact to Zubac's (LAL) arm that affects his layup attempt.
[Incidental or immaterial] Mudiay (DEN) enters the area inside the three-point line prior to the free throw being released.
Ingram (LAL) makes marginal contact with Barton (DEN) that does not affect his layup attempt.
Jokic (DEN) maintains legal guarding position on the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Williams (LAL).
[Detectable with stop watch] Ingram (LAL) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Zubac (LAL) jumps from point A to point B into the body of Chandler (DEN) and affects his shot attempt.
Faried (DEN) makes body to body contact with Ingram (LAL) that affects his shot attempt.
LHH shows Robinson (LAL) makes marginal contact with Chandler (DEN) that does not affect his SQBR.
Clarkson (LAL) commits a take foul on Chandler (DEN).
Faried (DEN) makes marginal contact with Williams (LAL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Young (LAL) steps out of bounds after receiving the inbound pass.
